00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.580
Globalization is a phenomenon that connects the world, 

00:00:03.581 --> 00:00:04.687
uniting nations, 

00:00:04.688 --> 00:00:06.250
economies and cultures. 

00:00:07.080 --> 00:00:09.493
Globalization is an economic, 

00:00:09.494 --> 00:00:10.138
social, 

00:00:10.139 --> 00:00:11.023
political, 

00:00:11.024 --> 00:00:15.528
technological and cultural process on a planetary scale 

00:00:15.529 --> 00:00:21.642
characterized by progressive integration and interaction between countries, 

00:00:21.643 --> 00:00:23.654
people and institutions. 

00:00:24.732 --> 00:00:25.297
That is, 

00:00:25.298 --> 00:00:29.637
it is a phenomenon that facilitates the exchange of ideas and goods. 

00:00:30.012 --> 00:00:35.120
Provides opportunities for economic growth and development. 

00:00:36.040 --> 00:00:42.699
s of globalization globalization also promotes global. 

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:48.449
This opens doors to new relations between countries and cultures. 

00:00:49.440 --> 00:00:50.585
In addition, 

00:00:50.586 --> 00:00:54.198
globalization favors cultural diversity, 

00:00:54.199 --> 00:00:57.281
exposing us to different cultures, 

00:00:57.282 --> 00:00:59.836
traditions and ways of life. 

00:01:00.833 --> 00:01:01.572
Finally, 

00:01:01.573 --> 00:01:05.516
globalization helps us to understand and accept 

00:01:05.517 --> 00:01:09.542
our differences by building a more united world. 

